{"type": "article", "id": 11277, "title": "Fido 宠物椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-26T07:15:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133953xSDJjnIZ0o4G6sQU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tFido 是椅子和狗窝的结合，来自意大利的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.ad-g.it/ver11\" target=\"_blank\">Davide G Aquin</a>i 通过观察狗狗们的行为，发现它们都想在主人身边，越近越好，于是发明了这款椅子。允许主人回到家后，坐在椅子上处理一些事情而无暇顾及自己宠物的时候，它们的窝就在脚边，还是可以近距离接触。<a href=\"http://www.ad-g.it/ver11/portfolio/fido-chair-and-pet-kennel/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里访问主页</a>\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133951U1v08oCaxJMkwrgX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133952cJuMosD3R5qWHybe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133952ciNpXM6Kus0tqWVf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span>\r\n\t\t\t</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\t\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\r\n\n\n"}